+++ b/README.md
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
-# Kahon
+# Taison
 
-A fork of Mihon, free and open source manga reader for Android.
+Taison is a fork of Kahon, which is itself a fork of Mihon, the free and open source manga reader for Android.
 
 ## Features
 
@@ -8,9 +8,12 @@ A fork of Mihon, free and open source manga reader for Android.
 * Increase max number of concurrent downloads from 2 to 16.
 * Trust all extensions by default.
 * Remove Google proprietary/privacy-unfriendly blobs (Firebase/Crashlytics).
+
+## Taison-specific enhancements
+
 * Streamlined library tab with hidden category tabs by default and a toolbar dropdown for quick category switching.
 * History tab can optionally scope entries to the active library category, both toggled under **Settings › Library › Categories**.
 
 ## Releases
 
-You can download Kahon releases from either [GitHub](https://github.com/AmanoTeam/Kahon/releases) or [F-Droid](https://f-droid.org/packages/com.amanoteam.kahon).
+You can download Taison releases from either [GitHub](https://github.com/AmanoTeam/Taison/releases) or [F-Droid](https://f-droid.org/packages/com.amanoteam.taison).
